data.description: Adorable & spotless one story home with Solar Panels located in the sought-after Valley Ranch! Boasting captivating curb appeal, a spacious layout and a prime location close to various amenities - this home is a must see! You will quickly notice the walls of windows allowing natural light to flood every living space throughout the home. The spacious kitchen includes a sizable breakfast bar, ideal for meal prepping or casual dining. With seamless connection to the breakfast nook and family room, this kitchen will quickly become the heart of the home. Retreat to the spacious master bedroom with an en suite and walk-in closet that will suit all your storage needs. Your backyard oasis is complete with a covered patio, lush grass, and plenty of yard space to enjoy the Texas weather. Just as clean as a New Construction home only better because of the seller's details, such as water softener, reverse osmosis, and amazing landscaping.  Save a Ton of Money with the PAID OFF Solar Panels.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this your next HOME SWEET HOME!
